    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>garam masala</strong>&nbsp;and <strong>cinnamon</strong>&nbsp;with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> on a plate</p>\r\n<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>chicken thighs</strong> to&nbsp;the plate and turn them several times until fully coated in all the spices</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
